(Duran Duran's "Girls On Film" playing)

507
00:19:51,011 --> 00:19:53,863
(Camels grunt)

508
00:19:53,865 --> 00:19:55,949
♪ see them walking hand in hand
across... ♪

509
00:19:55,951 --> 00:20:00,787
<i>My purse and I were making
the ultimate entrance.</i>

510
00:20:00,789 --> 00:20:05,041
♪ heads turning as the lights
flashing out are so bright ♪

